<div><div><h2>Future Enterprises acquires Ritvika Trading</h2></div><div>"homegrown retail major future enterprises said it has acquired ritvika trading.the company however did not provide financial details of the acquisition.the company has acquired 100 percent of equity share capital of trading firm ritvika trading pvt ltd future enterprises said in a filing to bse.shares of future enterprises closed at rs 43.75 per scrip on bse down 0.34 percent from its previous close."</div></div>